that were killed in battle.

00:05:01.563 --> 00:05:02.896
Exactly.

00:05:06.938 --> 00:05:11.188
You know that the Kodoku
are monitoring the participants?

00:05:14.271 --> 00:05:17.521
Well, they won't follow us inside.

00:05:18.105 --> 00:05:20.396
But the Kodoku are watching us.

00:05:21.230 --> 00:05:24.938
So they're the ones
who dispose of the dead bodies?

00:05:25.021 --> 00:05:27.896
Yes. They must be taking them somewhere.

00:05:28.563 --> 00:05:29.730
Which means?

00:05:30.813 --> 00:05:32.480
They have manpower and hiding spots

00:05:32.563 --> 00:05:36.146
to dispose of bodies across different
locations without getting caught.

00:05:36.230 --> 00:05:37.771
Excellent answer.

00:05:38.313 --> 00:05:40.438
If we can find
where the dead bodies are taken,

00:05:40.521 --> 00:05:43.146
maybe we can figure out
who is behind this game.

00:05:44.646 --> 00:05:47.146
So? I'm quite a strategist, right?

00:05:50.813 --> 00:05:53.521
So? Where do we start?

00:05:54.021 --> 00:05:57.396
First, we hunt for a candidate
to hand over to the police.

00:06:30.605 --> 00:06:33.980
