00:12:56.980 --> 00:13:03.063
If gods were real…
the world would be different.

00:13:20.813 --> 00:13:21.688
Good.

00:13:26.146 --> 00:13:27.521
Let's play.

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:41.188
Die, you bastard!

00:13:44.896 --> 00:13:46.855
Girls! Go for the girls!

00:13:46.938 --> 00:13:49.813
If you take their wooden tags,
I'll triple the pay!

00:14:20.355 --> 00:14:21.563
Move!

00:14:25.188 --> 00:14:27.230
Look who's caught now?

00:14:29.313 --> 00:14:31.438
What the hell's going on?

00:14:31.521 --> 00:14:32.938
This isn't what we were told!

00:14:33.021 --> 00:14:34.730
You can't leave. I'm paying you!

00:14:37.896 --> 00:14:38.813
Hey!

00:15:06.021 --> 00:15:08.980
Go! Hurry the hell up!

00:15:22.896 --> 00:15:25.063
Come on, go!

00:15:51.521 --> 00:15:53.105
Die!

00:16:14.688 --> 00:16:17.021
Someone! Go get the police!

00:16:18.355 --> 00:16:19.605
Out of the way!

00:16:52.063 --> 00:16:54.855
It's an offering to the gods.

00:17:10.730 --> 00:17:11.896
That's enough.

00:17:19.563 --> 00:17:21.480
Do I know you from somewhere?

00:17:21.563 --> 00:17:23.771
The police are on their way here.

00:17:23.855 --> 00:17:24.813
Yeah?

00:17:24.896 --> 00:17:26.313
So what?

00:17:26.396 --> 00:17:29.313
Those on the organizer's side
have high expectations for you two.

00:17:29.396 --> 00:17:31.480
