00:17:31.563 --> 00:17:33.646
You think I'll get caught?

00:17:34.521 --> 00:17:37.688
I can go ahead and cut you down here.

00:17:38.271 --> 00:17:39.688
Be my guest.

00:17:40.896 --> 00:17:43.855
If you think you can win
against this many rifles.

00:17:49.688 --> 00:17:51.021
I've lost interest.

00:18:00.521 --> 00:18:02.396
The times have changed.

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:04.438
There's no place left
for the samurai to live.

00:18:06.230 --> 00:18:10.605
You went through hell
after the war, didn't you?

00:18:13.271 --> 00:18:15.021
Bukotsu Kanjiya?

00:18:17.771 --> 00:18:20.230
It's none of your damn business.

00:18:51.021 --> 00:18:53.688
All right, then. Which one is it gonna be?

00:18:54.438 --> 00:18:58.105
What are you going to make us do?

00:18:58.188 --> 00:19:02.355
We're going to give one of you
to the police with your wooden tag.

00:19:02.938 --> 00:19:03.771
What?

00:19:05.313 --> 00:19:07.230
What? Wait a second…

00:19:07.855 --> 00:19:08.896
If you do that--

00:19:08.980 --> 00:19:12.188
Kodoku will kill you,
or the police will protect you.

00:19:12.271 --> 00:19:13.521
One or the other.

00:19:14.063 --> 00:19:14.896
What?

00:19:15.896 --> 00:19:18.021
And the one who isn't given to the police?

00:19:18.105 --> 00:19:20.438
We grab his wooden tag,
and he drops out right here.

00:19:23.271 --> 00:19:24.896
Hand me over to the police!

00:19:25.938 --> 00:19:27.105
I-I'll go!

00:19:27.188 --> 00:19:28.188
What?

00:19:28.271 --> 00:19:31.188
I'm the one who's going.
You keep your mouth shut!

00:19:33.688 --> 00:19:36.271
Well, I'm afraid you're
dropping out here, young man.

00:19:40.480 --> 00:19:43.105
Please. I'll do anything!

00:19:43.188 --> 00:19:46.605
Just accept it.
You've killed plenty already too.

00:19:46.688 --> 00:19:48.480
I haven't killed anyone at all!

00:19:48.563 --> 00:19:51.646
Even at Tenryuji Temple,
I just picked up a tag someone dropped.

00:19:51.730 --> 00:19:53.188
I'm sure… No lies, please.

00:19:53.271 --> 00:19:54.605
I'm not lying!

00:19:56.188 --> 00:19:58.813
This man threatened me.

00:20:00.105 --> 00:20:02.146
He told me he'd at least keep me alive.

00:20:02.230 --> 00:20:03.730
Stop lying!

00:20:07.271 --> 00:20:08.855
I come from a poor family.

00:20:10.021 --> 00:20:12.605
I joined because I wanted
to help my father's business.

00:20:16.646 --> 00:20:18.105
But then…

00:20:20.855 --> 00:20:22.521
It was a killing game…

00:20:25.896 --> 00:20:27.563
and I just couldn't do it.

00:20:32.021 --> 00:20:32.855
I'm begging you.

00:20:35.188 --> 00:20:38.896
Please… Please spare my life!

00:20:45.730 --> 00:20:47.438
You heard what he said.

00:20:55.855 --> 00:20:57.646
I guess you win.

00:20:59.646 --> 00:21:03.480
But you're gonna
lend me a hand in return, okay?

00:21:06.938 --> 00:21:08.438
Thank you.

00:21:11.063 --> 00:21:12.730
Thank you!

00:21:14.021 --> 00:21:14.855
What?

00:21:15.355 --> 00:21:16.688
Wait a minute.

00:21:16.771 --> 00:21:17.855
I can help you out too--

00:21:17.938 --> 00:21:21.105
Shujiro, you guys go and check
where the dead bodies are being taken.

00:21:21.188 --> 00:21:22.021
Okay.

00:21:22.605 --> 00:21:24.271
Oh, and you, Iroha.

00:21:25.105 --> 00:21:25.938
Here.

00:21:27.938 --> 00:21:28.980
What's this?

00:21:29.063 --> 00:21:30.396
It's a smoke ball.

00:21:30.480 --> 00:21:32.438
I don't need this.

00:21:32.521 --> 00:21:33.855
Just keep it with you.

00:21:34.438 --> 00:21:36.480
I'll call the police here.

00:21:36.563 --> 00:21:41.438
Use the commotion
to shake off the Kodoku watchers first.

00:21:41.980 --> 00:21:43.063
All right!

00:21:43.855 --> 00:21:46.980
Let's get this mission underway.

00:21:54.146 --> 00:21:54.980
Come in.

00:21:58.730 --> 00:22:00.230
